==English==
===Noun===
'''painter''' (''plural'' '''painters''')

# an [[artist]] who [[paint]]s pictures
# a [[laborer]] or workman who paints [[surface]]s using a [[paintbrush]] or other means
# {{nautical}} A [[rope]] connected to the [[bow]] of a boat, used to attach it to, e.g. a [[jetty]] or another boat.

